-3517063">Happier</a> 》，此前他在 2022 年与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">艾薇儿·拉维尼 (Avril Lavigne)</a>合作制作了《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/avril-lavigne-and-yungblud-team-up-on-emotional-new-collaboration-single-im-a-mess-listen-3342168">I&#39;m A Mess》</a> 。</p><p>与此同时，Lil Yachty（真名是 Miles Parks McCollum）出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/faye-webster">Faye Webster</a>最近的单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/faye-webster-announces-new-album-teams-up-with-lil-yachty-for-lego-ring-video-3570318">Lego Ring</a> ”中。他之前还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">Drake</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/flo-milli">Flo Milli</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future">Future</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/playboi-carti">Playboi Carti</a>等有过联系。</p><p>去年，Lil Yachty 推出了他的新专辑《Let&#39;s Start Here》，他在这张专辑中偏离了惯用的 trap 和说唱风格，转而偏向摇滚元素， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-yachty-lets-start-here-fuck-any-of-the-albums-i-dropped-before-this-one-3410547">他说这证明了“我可以做任何事情”</a> 。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/features/lil-yachty-lets-start-here-interview-sxsw-billboard-cover-story-1235281282/#recipient_hashed=87c91cb6f7c3bef8843b8e6fb6ffdcd835afd691d65df61a4fac92057c7f00dc&amp;recipient_salt=4ae5808f87b76ecdc83d2b728ac1c6c34add20ed3c6409345fd9815afa9fdc88" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a>采访时，他的非说唱灵感来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tame-impala">Tame Impala</a>的《Currents》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">Pink Floyd</a>的开创性歌曲《Dark Side Of The Moon》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-ocean">Frank Ocean</a>的《Blonde》。 </p><figure id="attachment_3575001" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3575001" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3575001" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/lil-yachty-ComplexCon.jpg" alt="莉尔·游艇" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.