ds/2021/07/palworld-game-screenshot-two-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/palworld-game-screenshot-two-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/palworld-game-screenshot-two-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在受到<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/pokemon">《口袋妖怪》</a></em>粉丝的关注后， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/palworld">Palworld</a></em>的总监公开反对“诽谤性评论”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/persona-3-reload-preview-interview-3571048">《女神异闻录 3：重装版》将成为必玩重制版</a></strong></li></ul><p>开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/pocketpair-inc">Pocketpair</a>的首席执行官兼<em>Palworld</em>的董事 Takuro Mizobe 在<a href="https://twitter.com/urokuta_ja/status/1749378276647485683" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X</a> （以前的 Twitter）上发布了针对该公司的抄袭和资产翻转指控（由<em><a href="https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/palworld-pokemon-plagiarism-accusations-pile-up-as-ceo-responds/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VGC</a>提供翻译）。</em></p><p> “除了看似死亡威胁的推文外，我们目前还收到针对我们艺术家的辱骂和诽谤性评论。虽然我们收到了有关<em>Palworld</em>的各种意见，但值得注意的是，与<em>Palworld</em>相关的所有材料的监督都是由包括我在内的团队进行的，”开发者在社交媒体平台上发帖称。</p><p> “我对所生产的材料承担责任。如果这些针对参与<em>Palworld</em>的艺术家的评论能够停止，我将不胜感激。” </p><figure id="attachment_3573901" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3573901" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3573901" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology.jpg" alt="Palworld：可以看到几个拿着机关枪的像羊一样的Pals" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.n